libgksu: libgksu (X Authorization Library)
libgksu: 
libgksu: Libgksu is a library from the gksu program that provides a simple API 
libgksu: for using su and sudo in programs that need to execute tasks as other 
libgksu: users. It provides X authentication facilities for running programs in 
libgksu: a X session.
